  ('optometrist-moex-03337', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於散瞳劑的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["散瞳劑不可能誘發閉鎖型青光眼急性發作", "散瞳劑普遍用在學童近視治療，所以完全沒有副作用，驗光人員皆可使用", "阿托品是長效散瞳劑，無論稀釋多少濃度到戶外都必須做紫外線防護，例如配戴太陽眼鏡", "所有散瞳劑藥效時間都一樣"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d48b9e09da91", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3dd3238e5460", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "112", "s": "1103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03338', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '視網膜檢影鏡（retinoscopy）檢查時，發現受測者右眼為兩個主軸在45度與135度方向的斜向散光，在 距離受測者眼前50 cm 處投射平行光源於受測眼，檢查者用右手由檢查者右上方往左下方斜向掃描受測 者眼睛，需要使用+1.00 D的鏡片達到中和點，檢查者再用右手由檢查者的左上方往右下方斜向掃描受測 者眼睛，需要使用-0.50 D的鏡片達到中和點。則受測者當時的屈光狀態為：', '["-1.00DS/-1.50DC×045", "-1.00DS/-1.50DC×135", "+1.00DS/-1.50DC×045", "+1.00DS/-1.50DC×135"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d48b9e09da91", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3dd3238e5460", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "112", "s": "1103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03339', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '若受測者在無調節狀況下直視遠方視標，且測者在前方33公分距離用外散光（divergent light）或套管擺 置下方（sleeve down）的設置進行視網膜檢影鏡檢查時看到逆動（against motion）。針對上述情形，下列', '["要中和此眼底反射光，必須縮短與受測者之間的距離", "此屈光不正為近視", "受測 者的近視低於3個屈光度", "僅"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d48b9e09da91", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3dd3238e5460", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "112", "s": "1103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03340', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '靜態視網膜檢影鏡檢查時，投射平行光，使用+1.00 D的鏡片，發現受測眼90度方向於50公分處可以看 到中和點。同樣使用+1.00 D的鏡片，180度方向於66.7公分處可以看到中和點。則受檢者的屈光狀態為：', '["-1.00DS/+0.50DC×090", "-1.00DS/+0.50DC×180", "-1.00DS/-0.50DC×090", "-1.00DS/-0.50DC×180"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d48b9e09da91", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3dd3238e5460", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "112", "s": "1103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03341', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '靜態視網膜檢影鏡檢查時，在距離受檢者眼前50 cm處投射平行光源於受測眼，同時兩眼都戴上+2.00 D 的鏡片。其視網膜反射光右眼呈現順動而左眼呈現逆動，則受檢者當時右眼及左眼的屈光狀態為：', '["右眼為遠視，左眼為近視", "右眼為近視，左眼為遠視", "右眼可能是低於2 D的近視，左眼為超過2 D的近視", "右眼可能是低於2 D的遠視，左眼為超過2 D的遠視"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d48b9e09da91", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3dd3238e5460", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "112", "s": "1103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03342', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '視網膜檢影鏡之工作距離，指的是患者的眼睛到視網膜檢影鏡的距離。當工作距離為50公分，且無工作 輔助鏡片時，若可用-4.00 D鏡片達到中和，則實際屈光度數為何？', '["-4.00 D", "-6.00 D", "-4.50 D", "-5.00 D"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d48b9e09da91", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3dd3238e5460", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "112", "s": "1103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03343', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '視網膜檢影鏡之工作距離，指的是患者的眼睛到視網膜檢影鏡的距離。當工作距離拉長到為67公分，且 未使用工作輔助鏡片，以鏡片-3.50DS/-1.50DC×180達到中和，則實際屈光度數為何？', '["-3.50DS/-1.50DC×180", "-3.50DS/-3.00DC×180", "-5.00DS/-1.50DC×180", "-5.00DS/-3.00DC×180"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d48b9e09da91", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3dd3238e5460", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "112", "s": "1103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL)
